Napoli lost 2-1 to Lazio in the Coppa Italia semi-final on Wednesday . 
  Napoli president Aurelio De Laurentiis has threatened to send his players to a training camp 'for an unlimited period of time' if they do not improve . 
  Rafael Benitez's side lost 1-0 at home in the semi-finals . 
  Lazio advanced to the final after winning the second leg on aggregate  . 
  Napoli have lost five games in a row and are sixth in Serie A . 
 